# Text Encryptor Challenge (English)

## Description
This is a web application for encrypting text. It uses Tailwind CSS for styling and plain javascript for the logic.

## Usage
Enter the text you want to encrypt in the input field and click on the 'Encrypt' button. The encrypted text will be displayed on the screen.

## Contributing
Pull requests are welcome. For major changes, please open an issue first to discuss what you would like to change.

